    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl08_LabelType\">You&rsquo;re skilled at learning the feel of a particular weapon after a few swings in combat.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl08_LabelType\">After your first attack with a weapon in which you are not proficient, the non-proficiency penalty decreases by 2 (to a &ndash;2 penalty). This effect lasts only while you have the weapon in hand; you must &ldquo;relearn&rdquo; the weapon each time you pick it up.</span><br /></span></p>",
